&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;121&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using documentation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;193&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reading and following installation, architectural and project documentation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
